---
name: detroit-rubyforge
version: 0.1.0

title  : Detroit RubyForge
summary: RubyForge plugin for Detroit

description:
  RubyForge plugin for Detroit build system. This plugin will
  upload a project's website to rubyforge.org during the publish
  phase. It should also post a release announce as a news items
  during the promote phase, however this functionailty current
  has a bug and needs to be fixed.

resources:
  home: http://detroit.github.com/
  code: http://github.com/detroit/detroit-rubyforge
  mail: http://groups.google.com/group/rubyworks-mailinglist

requirements:
  - detroit
  - forge

authors:
  - T. Sawyer <transfire@gmail.com>

